OL,3,CMan jailed for life for 'aiding and
OL,4,Cabetting' murder
OL,6,FA life sentence has been imposed upon
OL,7,Fa 28-year old man after he admitted
OL,8,F'aiding and abetting' the murder of
OL,9,FMalcolm McKeown.
OL,11,FThe 54-year-old victim was shot dead
OL,12,Fat he sat in a BMW parked at the rear
OL,13,Fof a service station in Waringstown on
OL,14,FAugust 19, 2019.
OL,16,FFour men were charged with murder and
OL,17,Fa trial began at Belfast Crown Court
OL,18,Flast week.
