OL,3,CMan jailed for life for 'aiding and
OL,4,Cabetting' murder
OL,6,FFollowing this, Mr Justice Fowler
OL,7,Fspoke to Martin and said: "As a result
OL,8,Fof your plea of guilty to murder,
OL,9,Fthere is only one sentence that I can
OL,10,Fimpose and that is a sentence of life
OL,11,Fimprisonment.
OL,13,F"However, a tariff hearing will be
OL,14,Fset, a date will be set for that and
OL,15,Fyou will be informed of that date in
OL,16,Fdue course."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/5
