OL,4,Cabetting' murder
OL,6,FWhen the non-jury hearing was opened
OL,7,Flast week, the Crown made the case
OL,8,Fthat Martin was one of two men
OL,9,Fcaptured on CCTV in Lurgan fleeing
OL,10,Ffrom a burned out Passat believed to
OL,11,Fhave been used in the murder.
OL,13,FMartin's three co-accused - 29-year-
OL,14,Fold Jake O'Brien from Rectory Road in
OL,15,FLurgan, 35-year-old Stevie Lee Watson
OL,16,Ffrom Princeton Avenue in Lurgan, and
OL,17,F34-year old Simon Smyth from
OL,18,FHazelgrove Avenue in Lurgan - continue
OL,19,Fto deny murdering Mr McKeown.
