OL,6,FIn light of Martin's plea, Crown
OL,7,Fbarrister Ciaran Murphy KC asked for
OL,8,Fthe case to be adjourned until Tuesday
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FThis request was granted by Mr Justice
OL,12,FFowler and as Martin was being led
OL,13,Ffrom the dock and into custody by
OL,14,Fprison staff, he waved at friends and
OL,15,Ffamily in the public gallery.
